1月23日，女性人权活动家[[塔瓦库·卡曼|塔瓦库·卡曼]](Tawakel Karman)被以“煽动动乱”和“组织非法的集会和游行”的罪名被拘留。<ref name="ifex_karman_freed">{{cite web | author =  | title = Authorities Release Journalists for Fear of Tunisia-Style Unrest | publisher = [[International_Freedom_of_Expression_Exchange|International Freedom of Expression Exchange]] | date = 26 January 2011 | url = http://www.ifex.org/yemen/2011/01/26/karman_released/ | accessdate = 1 February 2011 | archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/5wBItIgt2?url=http://www.ifex.org/yemen/2011/01/26/karman_released/ | archivedate = 2011-02-01 | deadurl = yes }}</ref> 她是萨那两个学生集会活动号召推翻Saleh政权的领导者。<ref name="aljaz_karman_detained"/> 她的丈夫说他不知道她的下落。<ref name="aljaz_karman_detained" /> 数千人举行示威以抗议逮捕Karman，另外一些抗议者则在检察院大楼前面举行静坐活动表达抗议。数百个学生在萨那大学外面举行抗议要求释放她。<ref name="aljaz_karman_detained" /> 她在被拘留30个小时后获得[[假释|假释]]，并被要求不得再违反“公共秩序和法律”。<ref name="ifex_karman_freed" /> 不过Karman在获释数小时后又继续参与了集会活动。<ref name="ifex_karman_freed" />

3月14日，安全部队突袭了一处4个西方记者聚集的地方并驱逐了他们。[[记者无国界|记者无国界]]组织谴责该事件，并表示两天前有另外两个外国记者曾遭到了驱逐。[[保护记者委员会|保护记者委员会]]同样谴责之，他们也表示有两个也门记者告诉他们——一组很可能是政府支持者组成的20人，在前一天曾来到位于萨那的记者部门威胁要烧光那里。<ref name="AJYemen15Mar">{{cite news | title = Yemen Deports Foreign Journalists | publisher = [[Al-Jazeera_English|Al-Jazeera English]] | url = http://english.aljazeera.net/news/middleeast/2011/03/2011314212132903514.html | date = 15 March 2011 | accessdate = 15 March 2011 | archive-date = 2011-03-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110315003511/http://english.aljazeera.net/news/middleeast/2011/03/2011314212132903514.html | dead-url = no }}</ref> 他们还说也门记者面临着持续的骚扰活动。<ref>{{cite web | author =  | title = Attacks on Journalists in Yemen, Sudan Amid Street Protests | url = http://cpj.org/2011/01/attacks-on-journalists-in-yemen-sudan-amid-street.php | publisher = [[Committee_to_Protect_Journalists|Committee to Protect Journalists]] | date =  | accessdate = 1 February 2011 | archive-date = 2011-02-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110201000655/http://cpj.org/2011/01/attacks-on-journalists-in-yemen-sudan-amid-street.php | dead-url = no }}</ref>

